OL,5, Renewed calls have been made for a     
OL,6, Hillsborough Law to ensure fairer      
OL,7, treatment for bereaved families.       
OL,9,FLiverpool City Region Mayor Steve      
OL,10,FRotheram and Greater Manchester Mayor  
OL,11,FAndy Burnham said the government needed
OL,12,Fto "level the scales of justice".      
OL,14,FIt comes after a TV drama telling the  
OL,15,Fstory of Anne Williams, whose son died 
OL,16,Fin the disaster, aired this week.      
OL,18,FThe government said it would engage    
OL,19,Fwith bereaved families and "carefully  
OL,20,Fconsider the points of learning".      
